{"_id":"wosTbl12edcbe233","name":"Wages of Sin - Complications","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","description":"<p>Complications table (d100) from Wages of Sin.</p>","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"wosR99136cdd3b","type":"text","name":"There is a family or personal relationship between the client and the target.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR5272665492","type":"text","name":"A local authority has imprisoned the target for unrelated crimes.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR3ff0085239","type":"text","name":"The target lives nomadically, with no fixed address.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR4abeebf256","type":"text","name":"The target has extensive combat training.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRf54cdcfabb","type":"text","name":"The target is in an active or imminent war zone.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR9a440de4f1","type":"text","name":"The target has an extensive network of friends in the area.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR0b12c81de6","type":"text","name":"A religious organization protects the target.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR48372f6a5e","type":"text","name":"The target is not guilty of the crime. They know who is.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR52e9ebfebf","type":"text","name":"The client is attempting to pin a crime on the target.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR041d45fa4b","type":"text","name":"An unknown force protects the target. They are unaware.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR1f97f82bb3","type":"text","name":"The target is embroiled in an unrelated sensitive legal matter which requires their full attention.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[11,11],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR28ee0b721f","type":"text","name":"The crew already knows the target.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR85ba0959ec","type":"text","name":"The client is many jumps away from the target and requires delivery.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[13,13],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRa6abc3ed34","type":"text","name":"Other victims pursue the target, seeking revenge for themselves.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[14,14],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR3fb5abf8e7","type":"text","name":"The target is able to morally justify their actions.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[15,15],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR1ee0824f69","type":"text","name":"The target is unaware of their 'crime' or the bounty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[16,16],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR60947e192c","type":"text","name":"The client is using the bounty as cover to pursue an unrelated agenda.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[17,17],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosReff477b8a7","type":"text","name":"The target protects themselves with their immense wealth.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[18,18],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR8a581eb6d5","type":"text","name":"Scant details on the target are available; significant investigative legwork is required.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[19,19],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR54b1ec8f4b","type":"text","name":"The target has many dependents.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[20,20],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR06085f14c0","type":"text","name":"The bounty has a strict, short time limit.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[21,21],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR6adad8c909","type":"text","name":"The lives of bystanders mean nothing to the target.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[22,22],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR28397d2252","type":"text","name":"Something inhuman pursues the target. It will not allow others to seize its quarry.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[23,23],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRc0e0cbb5c3","type":"text","name":"Prophetic visions plague the target. These visions are infectious, spreading to any in close physical proximity.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[24,24],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRf12a5c825f","type":"text","name":"The target is willing to trade valuable information for their freedom.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[25,25],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR41c386815b","type":"text","name":"The target is a member of a widespread fraternal organization.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[26,26],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR2386a03b20","type":"text","name":"A long-standing rivalry exists between the client and the target, who will make a counter-offer against the client if captured.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[27,27],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRe392afd50b","type":"text","name":"The target has an identical twin, clones, or commonplace aesthetic remodelling.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[28,28],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR98b9dd3fad","type":"text","name":"The target's crime was by order of a high-control group.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[29,29],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRa3500db4a7","type":"text","name":"The target has access to a jump-capable ship.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[30,30],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR16c1f691b8","type":"text","name":"The target is tying up loose ends, hoping to go into hiding.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[31,31],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR5c5c75dc9e","type":"text","name":"The client and the target are secretly the same person.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[32,32],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRfd6b8f61f5","type":"text","name":"The bounty stipulates the recovery of a related item alongside the target.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[33,33],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRfe7981384a","type":"text","name":"The bounty requires the crew not to kill anyone through action or inaction.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[34,34],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR6c775513b9","type":"text","name":"The instigating crime has a significant media following.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[35,35],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR0179b96bce","type":"text","name":"Everyone is unwilling to discuss the crime, target or client.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[36,36],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRa4cb3cc9f2","type":"text","name":"The target is a popular local celebrity.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[37,37],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR0f7d21eb7d","type":"text","name":"The population despises the client.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[38,38],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR1f188cbfa1","type":"text","name":"The population of the area is extremely hostile to all law enforcement, local or otherwise.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[39,39],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR5b928d6d77","type":"text","name":"The target has leverage over local forces and uses this to protect themselves.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[40,40],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR418029f823","type":"text","name":"The client is unwilling or unable to pay the bounty reward.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[41,41],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR8a0da6bccc","type":"text","name":"The target plans another crime at a major local event.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[42,42],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR416722200f","type":"text","name":"The target has evaded multiple bounty hunters.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[43,43],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR9ee3a49206","type":"text","name":"The bounty is to provide plausible deniability. The client does not want to see the crew succeed.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[44,44],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR511877fe8c","type":"text","name":"Upon the capture of the target, other parties try to bid on them.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[45,45],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR6934aa5428","type":"text","name":"The bounty requires no witnesses to the capture.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[46,46],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRee1d6bc435","type":"text","name":"The client offers access to experimental tools or weapons.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[47,47],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRce9c0bbb1d","type":"text","name":"A highly contagious disease ravages the body of the target.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[48,48],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRb51af57a26","type":"text","name":"The area is famous for its deadly flora/fauna.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[49,49],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR0ef174eece","type":"text","name":"The area is about to undergo a huge natural disaster.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[50,50],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR5a75359791","type":"text","name":"The location is under military occupation.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[51,51],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR672ed4de9e","type":"text","name":"The target has no digital footprint.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[52,52],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRbb71d828db","type":"text","name":"The target is a veteran, noted for their training in avoiding detection and capture.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[53,53],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR331e6b93d6","type":"text","name":"A documentary series starring the target is currently being filmed.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[54,54],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR9abdaa98d3","type":"text","name":"The client requires the crew to be filmed by a documentary crew throughout the process.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[55,55],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR5b59960810","type":"text","name":"The client only hires bounty hunters willing to undergo a certification process.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[56,56],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRdb6d0e89ad","type":"text","name":"The family of the target is extensive and extremely loyal.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[57,57],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR4b3470c2ad","type":"text","name":"The target has been hospitalized recently. The client is unaware.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[58,58],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR2893382150","type":"text","name":"A major conference (or similar event) is the only known public appearance of the target.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[59,59],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRd026e24960","type":"text","name":"The target is an avid collector of a rare and specific type of object.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[60,60],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR68c3310c70","type":"text","name":"The bounty requires an entire group of perpetrators be captured.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[61,61],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR5038d05bd8","type":"text","name":"The client wishes to see the target captured and humiliated in public.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[62,62],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRd63dc41d31","type":"text","name":"Beyond the bounty posting itself, there is no evidence of the client existing.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[63,63],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRc3bf725847","type":"text","name":"The client intends to rescind the bounty and blackmail the crew into more ethically dubious work.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[64,64],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR37678821e2","type":"text","name":"The target is widely reviled.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[65,65],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRa4d367169e","type":"text","name":"The inherent nature of the location is inimical to life.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[66,66],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR8bacce1c2b","type":"text","name":"Unbeknown to all, the target is an android.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[67,67],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR12af23df16","type":"text","name":"The payment for the bounty is in goods and services.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[68,68],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR3a80d017bc","type":"text","name":"The crew has previously seen the target die.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[69,69],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR2e16d9cd72","type":"text","name":"The target believes themselves under magical protection.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[70,70],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR9190504eca","type":"text","name":"The target is hiding in an extremely dense urban environment.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[71,71],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRec18ef3d6a","type":"text","name":"The target is hiding in a desolate, underpopulated wilderness or rural environment.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[72,72],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR43fbcf527d","type":"text","name":"The target has a series of hardened safe houses, each with supplies and weapons.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[73,73],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR79cb7b70f1","type":"text","name":"The client requires they are present throughout the process. They require protection.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[74,74],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR22339fb596","type":"text","name":"The target is trying to kill the client. If successful, there is no one to pay the crew.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[75,75],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRd739928ab5","type":"text","name":"The target would die before being taken alive.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[76,76],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR42728ea349","type":"text","name":"The associates of the target will seek revenge for any harm.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[77,77],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRd0538a4d80","type":"text","name":"The target is heavily involved in a popular, pro-social cause. Without them the efforts are likely to fail.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[78,78],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR867283fc20","type":"text","name":"The target is charismatic. They inspire extreme loyalty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[79,79],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR1788a8d9d0","type":"text","name":"85% of the target's body has been cybernetically enhanced.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[80,80],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRf061c13bcf","type":"text","name":"The target has planted false rumours and red herrings as to their own location.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[81,81],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR15fc323419","type":"text","name":"The target is always outlandishly dressed and highly recognizable.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[82,82],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRd87d60b36f","type":"text","name":"The target has moles in the client's organization.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[83,83],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR4596256f7a","type":"text","name":"This bounty is a job interview for the real bounty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[84,84],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR7d487fda63","type":"text","name":"The client needs the target for a human sacrifice.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[85,85],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRb972537a8b","type":"text","name":"The target is the final living witness of something terrible.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[86,86],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR67316f0a19","type":"text","name":"The target is an experimental subject or specimen. The bounty is a cover for their return.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[87,87],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR92e5435076","type":"text","name":"The target holds huge debts. The debtors try to collect any outstanding debt from the killers.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[88,88],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR54d7b01cd2","type":"text","name":"The target has the ability to feign death.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[89,89],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRddeb5cbb9c","type":"text","name":"The target had powerful dreams of a strange entity, ethereal yet heavy. They have made a pact with this being.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[90,90],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR31af293b19","type":"text","name":"The target habitually marks their passing in an idiosyncratic way.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[91,91],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR12f57150b6","type":"text","name":"Local law enforcement protects the target.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[92,92],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR663f9f589d","type":"text","name":"The target is a high level employee at a major local corporation.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[93,93],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR3659313c2f","type":"text","name":"A major union organiser, the wider organization protects the target.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[94,94],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR19520333fa","type":"text","name":"A member of the largest local criminal organization is closely related to the target.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[95,95],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR6d05dc5d40","type":"text","name":"The target curses their slayer or captor.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[96,96],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR2a82dae5ab","type":"text","name":"The influence of a local politician protects the target. The two are old friends.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[97,97],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR510a1559c5","type":"text","name":"The target does not eat. They feed upon the dreams of others, projecting their hunger outwards as a spectral maw.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[98,98],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRc7dfa0c3c1","type":"text","name":"The target is convinced their capture or death would doom worlds.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[99,99],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR0a6496d0f1","type":"text","name":"The target is no more. Something has consumed them, and now wears their likeness as a skin-suit. They move among their prey once more.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"drawn":false}],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":1300,"_stats":{"systemId":"mosh","systemVersion":"0.6.1","coreVersion":"14","createdTime":1753101600000,"modifiedTime":1753101600000,"lastModifiedBy":"wos_module_init"},"schemaVersion":"13.341"}
