{"_id":"wosTbl4613b79127","name":"Wages of Sin - Bounty Level & Rewards","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","description":"<p>Bounty Level & Rewards table from Wages of Sin (pg. 12-13).</p>","formula":"1d9","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"wosR638bebf62a","type":"text","name":"BL:1 - Minor Bounties (Payscale: 1D10KCR) - Minor issues for organizations. Big problems for desperate civilians.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRa0a20fed32","type":"text","name":"BL:2 - Lesser Bounties (Payscale: 1D5X10KCR) - Bounties on people who do not want to be found.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR1c4d0a4c26","type":"text","name":"BL:3 - Serious Bounties (Payscale: 1D10X10KCR) - Targets with experience or resources and the will to use them.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR3daa1ee267","type":"text","name":"BL:4 - Dangerous Bounties (Payscale: 1D5X100KCR) - Targets with experience and resources. They will kill you.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR74b6081903","type":"text","name":"BL:5 - Major Bounties (Payscale: 1D10X100KCR) - High-power targets or those outside normal social context.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR54a7d8bed4","type":"text","name":"BL:6 - Operational Bounties (Payscale: 1D5MCR) - Those protected by organized violence.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosRbace723bef","type":"text","name":"BL:7 - Strategic Bounties (Payscale: 1D10MCR) - The linchpins of organizations or those who wield terrible power directly.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR804562edba","type":"text","name":"BL:8 - Legendary Bounties (Payscale: 2D10MCR) - Household names or those at the secret loci of power.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wosR48eedb45c2","type":"text","name":"BL:9 - Apocalyptic Bounties (Payscale: 1D100MCR) - Names that are only whispered. Senior executives. Rogue AI.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false}],"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":1000,"_stats":{"systemId":"mosh","systemVersion":"0.6.1","coreVersion":"14","createdTime":1753101600000,"modifiedTime":1753101600000,"lastModifiedBy":"wos_module_init"},"schemaVersion":"13.341"}
